<p>113.18. <b>Not Accepted 
</b></p>
<p>See 113.1. 
</p>
<p>To date, the death penalty is still maintained in the laws of Brunei Darussalam. 
</p>
<p>Furthermore, its abolition is not required by international law. 
</p>
