<p>113.29. <b>Accepted 
</b></p>
<p>Brunei Darussalam ratified the CRC on 27 December 1995.  Furthermore, Brunei 
</p>
<p>Darussalam submitted its combined second and third periodic reports to the 
</p>
<p>Committee on the Rights of the Child in October 2013. 
</p>
<p>113.30. <b>Accepted</b> 
</p>
<p>113.31. <b>Accepted</b> 
</p>
<p>113.32. <b>Accepted</b> 
</p>
<p>113.33. <b>Not Accepted 
</b></p>
