<p>113.137. <b>Not Accepted 
</b></p>
<p>See 113.41.  Children and Young Persons Act (Cap 219) prohibits a child from 
</p>
<p>being sentenced or ordered to be imprisoned for any offence or be committed to 
</p>
<p>prison in default of payment or fine or cost. 
